{"tid":458210,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點先減得走對肥仔波","createTime":"2017-11-04T15:37:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-05T08:35:49.000Z","uid":89985,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a20f3d84851178051cb81329e8a392c242815cf5","tid":458210,"uid":89985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:37:35.000Z","msg":"就算瘦返 對肥仔波依然存在 仲要向外下垂<br />\n有次俾女神恥笑我點解唔戴返個胸圍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba9e0326cd1eb1e486b1d99b339f46b16b79ed2","tid":458210,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:41:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n肥仔波聽講有兩種<br />\n一種係荷爾蒙問題 一種係肥<br />\n肥既肥仔波或者可以減<br />\n但向外下垂應該真係荷爾蒙問題<br />\n要做手術乳腺切除 冇得運動減<br />\n手術應該都要好多錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3ff88ff5544bd712d2c3662198cb10502814a1f","tid":458210,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:43:06.000Z","msg":"本身瘦底<br />\n但而家肥到有肥仔波同肚腩<br />\n<br />\n四肢無肉<br />\n<br />\n點搞"},{"pid":"ebec877dbcb940cfcdfebdcf94df7c61a6a2feed","tid":458210,"uid":134171,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:45:37.000Z","msg":"肥仔波有兩種<br />\n一種減唔到要做手術"},{"pid":"6a0d764e4a36d4623cd804bd22d1e0daa3c66941","tid":458210,"uid":135735,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:48:07.000Z","msg":"肥仔波點都減唔曬，利申以前好肥減完之後就有些少肥仔波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做完gym而家有少少胸肌但肥仔波都仲係到 但係係唔覺眼嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97776c9fd313f73d8a7261afd70ecf0f201fa228","tid":458210,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-04T15:55:17.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥仔波點都減唔曬，利申以前好肥減完之後就有些少肥仔波<img src=\"/asse